h1. Features

<div class="summary">
<p>Gecode/R provides access to many, but not all, of "Gecode's 
features":http://www.gecode.org/gecode-doc-latest/modules.html.</p>
</div>

h2. Supported Gecode features 

The following things are supported by Gecode/R.

* "Boolean variables and constraints":http://www.gecode.org/gecode-doc-latest/group__TaskIntIntBool.html
* Finite domain integer variables with the following constraints
** "Arithmetic":http://www.gecode.org/gecode-doc-latest/group__TaskIntIntArith.html
** "Cardinality":http://www.gecode.org/gecode-doc-latest/group__TaskIntIntCard.html without global cardinality
** "Channel":http://www.gecode.org/gecode-doc-latest/group__TaskIntIntChannel.html
** "Distinct":http://www.gecode.org/gecode-doc-latest/group__TaskIntIntDistinct.html
** "Domain":http://www.gecode.org/gecode-doc-latest/group__TaskIntIntDomain.html
** "Element":http://www.gecode.org/gecode-doc-latest/group__TaskIntIntElement.html
** "Linear":http://www.gecode.org/gecode-doc-latest/group__TaskIntIntLinear.html
** "Simple relation":http://www.gecode.org/gecode-doc-latest/group__TaskIntIntRel.html
** "Sorting":http://www.gecode.org/gecode-doc-latest/group__TaskIntIntSort.html
* Finite integer sets with the following constraints
** "Distinct":http://www.gecode.org/gecode-doc-latest/group__TaskIntSetDistinct.html
** "Domain":http://www.gecode.org/gecode-doc-latest/group__TaskIntSetDom.html
** "Connection constraints to finite domain variables":http://www.gecode.org/gecode-doc-latest/group__TaskIntSetConnect.html
** "Relation":http://www.gecode.org/gecode-doc-latest/group__TaskIntSetRel.html
** "Set selection":http://www.gecode.org/gecode-doc-latest/group__TaskIntSetSelection.html
** "Set operation":http://www.gecode.org/gecode-doc-latest/group__TaskIntSetRelOp.html
* Branching selection
* Depth first search search
* Reification and propagation strength
* Branch and bound search

h2. Features not supported

The following are some notable features that are included in Gecode but _not_
in Gecode/R (but might be in the future).

* Unsupported integer constraints
** "Regular":http://www.gecode.org/gecode-doc-latest/group__TaskIntIntRegular.html
** "Global cardinality":http://www.gecode.org/gecode-doc-latest/group__TaskIntIntCard.html
** "Scheduling":http://www.gecode.org/gecode-doc-latest/group__TaskIntIntScheduling.html
* Unsupported set constraints
** "Convexity":http://www.gecode.org/gecode-doc-latest/group__TaskIntSetConvex.html
** "Sequence":http://www.gecode.org/gecode-doc-latest/group__TaskIntSetSequence.html
** "Projector":http://www.gecode.org/gecode-doc-latest/group__TaskIntSetProjector.html
* Limited discrepancy search
* Custom propagators and branching strategies
